---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="VALE Itabira Complex — Verified GHG Reduction | Rentar"
  description="Independent laboratory verification of the Rentar Fuel Catalyst at the VALE Itabira Complex in Brazil. Verified GHG emissions reduction on CAT 793F Off Highway Trucks."
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:45vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">Independent Laboratory Verification</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;">VALE Itabira Complex</h1>
      <p>Verified GHG emissions reduction on CAT 793F Off Highway Trucks. Field validated at one of the world's largest iron ore mining operations in Minas Gerais, Brazil.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="split-content">
          <p class="section-label">Case Study</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Verified emissions reduction in open-pit mining</h2>
          <p class="section-text">The Rentar Fuel Catalyst was installed on Caterpillar 793F Off Highway Trucks at the VALE Itabira Complex, one of the world's largest iron ore mining operations. Emissions testing was conducted by an independent third-party laboratory using a before/after protocol to quantify the GHG emissions reduction attributable to the Rentar Fuel Catalyst.</p>
          <p class="section-text">The testing validated measurable reductions in greenhouse gas emissions with the Rentar Fuel Catalyst installed, demonstrating the technology's effectiveness under real-world open-pit mining conditions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="split-image" style="background:transparent; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
          <iframe src="/images/vale_ghg_reduction" style="width:100%; max-width:960px; height:480px; border:0;" title="VALE GHG Reduction Visualization" loading="lazy"></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Test Configuration</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Validation parameters</h2>
      <div class="val-specs" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); margin-bottom:32px;">
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Test Platform</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">CAT 793F OHT</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Engine</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">CAT 175-16</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Verification Method</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">Before / After</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Laboratory</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">Independent Third Party</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="val-ribbon" style="padding:0;">
        <span class="val-badge val-badge--active">Verified</span>
        <span class="val-badge val-badge--active">Laboratory Tested</span>
        <span class="val-badge val-badge--active">Field Validated</span>
        <span class="val-badge">Third Party</span>
        <span class="val-badge">Patent Protected</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label">Key Findings</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">What the testing confirmed</h2>
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>The independent laboratory testing at VALE Itabira confirmed that the Rentar Fuel Catalyst delivered measurable reductions in greenhouse gas emissions on Caterpillar 793F Off Highway Trucks operating in open-pit iron ore mining conditions.</p>
        <p class="manifesto-highlight">"The Rentar Fuel Catalyst was successfully validated at the VALE Itabira Complex in Brazil with verified reductions in GHG emissions."</p>
        <p>The before/after protocol used by the independent laboratory provides a rigorous basis for quantifying the emissions reduction attributable to the Rentar technology. Results were measured under real operating conditions at one of the world's most demanding mining sites.</p>
        <p>This independent validation adds to the growing body of evidence demonstrating the Rentar Fuel Catalyst's effectiveness across multiple industries, equipment types, and operating environments.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:40px; text-align:center;">
        <a href="/downloads/RENTAR-SITECH_Reference_Letter.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Download Reference Letter</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--navy); text-align:center;">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Next steps</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--white);">Deploy the Rentar Fuel Catalyst at your operation</h2>
      <p class="section-text" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom:40px;">Schedule a consultation with our engineering team to evaluate your fleet and design a validation program for your specific equipment and operating conditions.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact sales</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
